&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>함수와 연산&lt;br>
Sass는 다양한 내장 함수와 수학적 연산을 지원한다:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-scss" data-lang="scss">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nv">$base-size&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">px&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nc">.container&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// 수학적 연산
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">padding&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">$base-size&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mf">.5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
